programme.title: Lensa : Panorama Ep19
programme.desc: Gading Kenyir - Kenyir Elephant Conservation Village (KECV) merupakan satu lokasi bagi memelihara spesis haiwan mamalia ini yang dibina pada tahun 2012. Terletak di Tasik Kenyir, Hulu Terengganu, pusat konservasi ini berkeluasan 256 hektar atau 600 ekar, di mana hanya 10 peratus dari kawasan ini dibuka bagi aktiviti pelancongan. programme.desc: Program doku-travelog yang membincangkan senibina tradisional rumah-rumah tradisi yang terdapat di Malaysia. Rancangan 13 episod, mewakili 13 negeri di Malaysia, dengan 13 jenis Rumah Tradisional yang terpilih dari setiap negeri, turut menggunakan model 3D rumah tradisional yang telah dihasilkan menjadi sebahagian pengisian rancangan ini, melalui animasi. Hos Intan Norsaina. Dalam episod ini Pengacara Intan Norsaina membawa para penonton ke Rumah Brunei Sabah.

programme.title: The Gadis Ep04
programme.desc: Nad berjaya memujuk Lisa sekali lagi untuk pergi ke KL menjadi Sugarbaby. Lisa keluar dengan seorang Dato yang sanggup berbelanja besar, Lisa mahu mengumpul wang sebanyak mungkin bagi melanjutkan pelajarannya. Malam tersebut Lisa tidak balik rumah, dia berbohong kepada Lina kononnya dia tidur di rumah Rocky. Nad dan Mika merancang untuk menjual Lisa yang masih dara dengan harga yang tinggi bagi menyelesaikan hutang mereka. Mika telah meletakkan dadah dalam minuman Lisa, menyebabkan Lisa tidak sedarkan diri. Rancangan mereka gagal pada malam itu kerana Dato tersebut tidak mampu membayar harga yang tinggi seperti dijanjikan. Apabila Lisa tersedar, Mika berpura-pura mengatakan yang Dato itu cuba mengambil kesempatan kepada Lisa dan Mika telah menyelamatkannya. Lisa terhutang budi dengan Mika. Nad telah membuat satu lagi temujanji dengan seorang Dato bernama Dato Jefri. Melihat Dato Jefri, Lisa terkejut kerana dia tidak seperti Dato sebelum ini. Dato Jefri jauh lebih muda dan kacak, dia seorang duda kematian isteri. Dato Jefri terdengar Lisa masih bersekolah dan akan mengambil peperiksaan SPM

programme.title: Superbike
programme.desc: Ia berkisar tentang kehidupan seharian sekumpulan penunggang motosikal superbike yang menggelar kumpulan mereka sebagai 'Pirate Bikers' dan diketuai oleh Bugs (Kamal Adli). Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.title: Azem 2
programme.desc: Beberapa orang membawa seorang gadis yang dirasuk teruk dengan kotak kayu berkunci untuk menyembuhkannya.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Pegawai penguatkuasa undang-undang Bunian 444 atau juga dikenali sebagai Black sedang diburu kerana rakan setugasnya seorang penderhaka, 419, telah melarikan diri ke dunia manusia. Menyedari 419 telah menghuni tubuh manusia, Black memutuskan untuk memasuki tubuh Malik untuk bersaing dengannya. Pada mata manusia, 'Malik' telah terselamat daripada kematian dengan menakjubkan sekali dan akibat kejadian itu dia telah hilang ingatan. Dalam pada itu, Sofia mula menyedari yang 'Malik' merupakan buat hatinya semasa kecil dan dia diselubungi rasa bersalah kerana telah meletak Malik dalam situasi bahaya. Namun 'Malik' sekarang ialah Black - biadab, mementingkan diri sendiri dan tekad dengan satu tujuan dalam misinya. Adakah dia akan ingat siapa Sofia sebenarnya? Black mendapati dirinya berdepan dengan pembunuhan yang mengerikan semasa dia cuba mengharungi dunia manusia. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang lelaki yang penuh misteri muncul dan membayangi setiap gerak-gerinya.

programme.title: Langsuir
programme.desc: Azlan dan rakan-rakannya sedang bercuti, melawat pulau larangan Pulau Langsuir. Di sana, Azlan bertemu Suri, seorang gadis cantik, dan jatuh cinta kepadanya. Dia tidak tahu bahawa Suri adalah hantu 'langsuir' yang mendiami pulau itu. Iri hati dengan hubungan percintaan mereka, rakan-rakan Azlan merancang untuk menikam kepala Suri dengan paku untuk mendedahkan bentuk hantunya. Ini hanya membawa huru-hara kepada kumpulan itu kerana rancangan mereka telah menimbulkan kemarahan kakak Suri, Dewi.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Apabila salah seorang pemandu trak tunda muncul mati dan seorang lagi masih hilang, Detektif Fadil dari balai polis tempatan mula membuat hubungan antara kes terbarunya dan Losmen Melati. Dia mula bertanya soalan dan menghantar orang barunya, Osman, menyamar untuk mengetahui apa yang sebenarnya berlaku di losmen misteri itu. Tetapi apabila Osman hilang, Fadil bergegas ke losmen untuk mencarinya, hanya untuk melencong apabila dia melihat sesosok bayangan gelap di jalan raya di hadapannya, menyebabkan dia terbabas. Fadil sedar ada sesuatu yang lebih besar sedang bermain.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 5 Ep5
programme.desc: Melati mendedahkan niat sebenar dia yang ingin mengembalikan anaknya dari kematian. Dengan bantuan seorang Bomoh, Watih, Melati akan membawa pulang anaknya menggunakan darah yang dicuri daripada tetamu mudanya yang telah meninggal dunia sebelum ini. Namun, bukan anaknya sahaja yang ingin dibawa pulang. Melati telah membuat keputusan untuk membawa kembali Sigit - lelaki yang dibesarkannya, seorang lelaki yang mempunyai masa lalu yang kelam dan tragis - Melati percaya bahawa di sebalik kengerian masa lalunya, dia layak mendapat peluang kedua. Makhluk jahat yang pernah terperangkap di ruang bawah tanah didedahkan di Kusno, makhluk jahat dan jahat serta bapa Sigit. Apabila Kusno mula membunuh, dia mula menjadi lebih kuat dan mula menyerupai bentuk manusianya sekali lagi. Kusno mempunyai satu misi untuk memusnahkan Melati. Tetapi Kusno tidak bersendirian. Dengan menggunakan kuasanya yang semakin meningkat, dia memihak kepada bentuk jahat lelaki yang membunuh ibu Melati pada tahun 1900-an - Pemburu.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Selepas lebih satu abad, Melati akhirnya bertemu semula dengan anaknya, Ari. Ari mula mengingati masa lalunya dan bagaimana dia mati. Melati mendedahkan kebenaran Sigit dan Kusno. Walaupun Melati berharap peluang kedua akan menjadikan dia lelaki yang lebih baik, Watih masih tidak mempercayai Sigit. Dia memberi amaran kepadanya bahawa jika dia bertindak menentang Melati dan keluarganya, dia mempunyai kuasa untuk merobek jiwanya dari tubuh barunya. Sara, seorang detektif polis dari bandar dan rakan keluarga Fadil bimbang tentang dia selepas radionya senyap dan memutuskan untuk menjelajah ke negara itu untuk memastikan dia baik-baik saja. Dengan semua tanda menunjuk kepada Losmen Melati, Sara menuju ke rumah terkutuk itu. Semasa Watih berlepas dari Losmen Melati, dia diserang oleh Kusno. Dia membunuh Watih, membalas dendam pertamanya.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Melati, Golok, Sigit dan Ari bersiap sedia untuk melawan Kusno. Sara memasuki losmen mencari Fadil tetapi akhirnya terperangkap di salah satu bilik. Di sana, dia mendapati Fadil terperangkap dalam perigi dari episod 4. Diserang oleh roh rumah, Sara cuba menyelamatkan Fadil dan akhirnya mengorbankan dirinya dalam proses itu. Melati meyakinkan arwah rumah untuk berpihak kepadanya dalam perjuangannya menentang Kusno. Kusno dan Pemburu menyerang Losmen Melati. Sigit berbaik semula dengan Ari atas kengerian masa lalunya dan menentang ayahnya untuk kebaikan. Kini keluar dari perigi, Fadil cuba keluar dari rumah tetapi tersedut untuk melawan Kusno. Berjuang melawan Kusno sendiri, Fadil berada di ambang kematian apabila Kusno menggigitnya, membiarkan kutukan memasuki sistemnya. Apabila semua kelihatan hilang untuk Melati, dia mendedahkan senjata rahsianya - Watih, yang Kusno dipercayai telah mati, kembali untuk memberikan pukulan maut terakhir, akhirnya mengalahkan Kusno sekali dan untuk selama-lamanya. Namun apabila hari baru menjelma, Fadil muncul semula, tetapi semuanya tidak seperti yang disangka. Mata Fadil menjadi hitam, membayangkan kisah Losmen Melati belum berakhir.

programme.title: You Saka… Pergi Jauh-jauh Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Nia yang baru bangun pagi kelihatan gelisah akibat mimpi tuan puteri ingin memberikannya sekuntum bunga dan dia menceritakan kepada Shasa. Shasa hanya menyatakan kerana Nia terbawa-bawa dan memikirkan yang dia alami. Sementara itu, Pak Abas dan Roslan bercakap tentang arwah Rosserita. Di pejabat, Nia diganggui oleh saka Gelam. Manakala di rumah dia terserempak depan berdepan dengan lembaga putih berdialog dan memberi amaran kepadanya. Kemudiannnya menceritakan pengalamannya bahawa lembaga putih itu menyerupai emaknya. Manakala Fauzan dengan ibunya bertengkar kerana ibunya bercadang untuk menghantar ke hospital gila. Ini berikutan Fauzan bercakap dengan seseorang kononnya berada di atas bangku disebelahnya.

programme.title: Azem 3
programme.desc: Seorang isteri cemburu "zehra" meragui suaminya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan rakannya, dia merancang untuk melaksanakan sihir hitam oleh beberapa syeikh yang jahat untuk mendapatkan suaminya kembali daripada pesaingnya. Beberapa siri peristiwa hebat mula berlaku kepada rakannya berakhir dengan pembunuhan "zehra" y suaminya untuk mengelakkan skandal curang.

programme.title: Algojo: Perang Santet
programme.desc: Desta dilahirkan dalam keluarga bahagia. Namun, kebahagiaan dalam keluarga tidak kekal lama apabila hantaran sihir membawa kepada kematian kedua ibu bapa. Desta membesar menjadi seorang yang menyendiri dan penuh misteri. Keinginannya untuk membalas dendam membuatkan dia mencari dalang di sebalik kematian ibu bapanya.

programme.title: Langsuir
programme.desc: Azlan dan rakan-rakannya sedang bercuti, melawat pulau larangan Pulau Langsuir. Di sana, Azlan bertemu Suri, seorang gadis cantik, dan jatuh cinta kepadanya. Dia tidak tahu bahawa Suri adalah hantu 'langsuir' yang mendiami pulau itu. Iri hati dengan hubungan percintaan mereka, rakan-rakan Azlan merancang untuk menikam kepala Suri dengan paku untuk mendedahkan bentuk hantunya. Ini hanya membawa huru-hara kepada kumpulan itu kerana rancangan mereka telah menimbulkan kemarahan kakak Suri, Dewi.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.desc: Beberapa orang membawa seorang gadis yang dirasuk teruk dengan kotak kayu berkunci untuk menyembuhkannya.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Pegawai penguatkuasa undang-undang Bunian 444 atau juga dikenali sebagai Black sedang diburu kerana rakan setugasnya seorang penderhaka, 419, telah melarikan diri ke dunia manusia. Menyedari 419 telah menghuni tubuh manusia, Black memutuskan untuk memasuki tubuh Malik untuk bersaing dengannya. Pada mata manusia, 'Malik' telah terselamat daripada kematian dengan menakjubkan sekali dan akibat kejadian itu dia telah hilang ingatan. Dalam pada itu, Sofia mula menyedari yang 'Malik' merupakan buat hatinya semasa kecil dan dia diselubungi rasa bersalah kerana telah meletak Malik dalam situasi bahaya. Namun 'Malik' sekarang ialah Black - biadab, mementingkan diri sendiri dan tekad dengan satu tujuan dalam misinya. Adakah dia akan ingat siapa Sofia sebenarnya? Black mendapati dirinya berdepan dengan pembunuhan yang mengerikan semasa dia cuba mengharungi dunia manusia. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang lelaki yang penuh misteri muncul dan membayangi setiap gerak-gerinya.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep 15 Ep15
programme.desc: Seekers Underground menampilkan penyelidik paranormal dan jurugambar profesional, Syai yang akan bergandingan dengan Amir, seorang psikik yang mampu melihat dan berhubung dengan alam ghaib. Duo ini akan bekerjasama dengan ahli paranormal tempatan yang lain untuk mendapat akses ke tempat-tempat berhantu dan luar biasa di Malaysia.

programme.title: Bohsia 2: Jalan Kembali
programme.desc: Tasha adalah seorang gadis yang dibesarkan tanpa keluarga dan pendidikan, memaksanya untuk mencari perlindungan di dunia bawah tanah, di kalangan samseng jalanan. Dia tidak lama kemudian menjadi bosan dengan kehidupannya yang tidak bermakna, tetapi jalannya menuju penebusan adalah jalan yang diturap dengan banyak halangan.

programme.title: Congkak
programme.desc: Kisahnya bermula apabila Kazman serta isterinya Sufiah mengambil keputusan bercuti bersama dua anaknya, Lisa dan Ely di sebuah banglo di tepi tasik. Kazman sudah berjanji dengan seorang kawannya untuk membeli banglo tersebut sebagai persinggahan semasa bercuti. Pelbagai peristiwa pelik berlaku sepanjang perjalan mereka termasuk kehilangan telefon bimbitnya. Setibanya mereka di banglo tersebut, peristiwa yang semakin pelik turut terjadi. Sufiah cuba meyakinkan Kazman untuk keluar dari rumah tersebut tetapi tidak diendahkan. Kazman tetap berkeras untuk membeli rumah tersebut kerana sudah berjanji dengan kawannya. Sufiah sentiasa merasakan ada makhluk sedang memerhatikannya. Salah seorang anak mereka, Lisa setiap malam akan turun ke sebuah bilik gelap untuk bermain congkak dengan seseorang yang hanya boleh dilihat olehnya seorang. Sufiah yang tidak boleh bersabar dengan perkara itu telah membuang congkak tersebut ke dalam tasik. Lisa juga sentiasa bermain di tepi belukar di belakang rumah kerana kawannya tinggal di situ sehingga Kazman perasan Lisa bermain menghadap kubur lama. Pada malam keesokannya, Sufiah dikejutkan lagi dengan bunyi congkak tersebut dari bilik yang sama. Apabila Sufiah pergi melihat, dilihatnya seorang tua sedang bemain congkak tersebut. Semakin lama peristiwa yang berlaku semakin pelik dan menyeramkan sehingga pada malam ketiga kedua-dua anaknya telah hilang dan Sufiah didapati tidur di siling bilik. Pak Tua, penduduk paling lama di kampung itu telah pergi ke rumah tersebut untuk menyelamatkan keluarga Kazman dan mencari Ely dan Lisa. Apakah sejarah sebenar banglo tersebut dan dapatkan Sufiah diselamatkan serta berjayakah Ely dan Lisa ditemui semula.

programme.title: Ghost Writer 2
programme.desc: Kejayaan novel keduanya mengharumkan nama Naya. Malangnya dia lebih dilabelkan sebagai psikik daripada penulis. Ini membuatkan Naya geram dan berat hati untuk berhadapan dengan dunia berhantu itu semula. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila bakal suaminya Vino meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 3 Ep3
programme.desc: Black mula seronok berada dalam badan manusianya. Namun menghuni tubuh badan manusia ialah jenayah Kelas A dalam dunia Bunian - Black menerima kata dua - dia mesti dapat mencari 419 atau menerima hukuman yang paling menggerunkan. Meskipun begitu, satu lagi kes pembunuhan yang mengerikan telah berlaku, sama seperti kejadian baru-baru ini. Nampaknya mangsa seperti ada kaitan dengan Aisya. Lelaki dengan wajah berparut muncul untuk menyeksanya ... siapa dia dan kenapa Aisya mengikut arahannya? Sofia dapat tahu yang mungkin ayahnya telah dibunuh dan ini membawanya kepada CEO Insurans Mahkota, Lokman Nazir, yang boleh mendapatkan fail lama ayahnya ... dan mungkin menjadi petunjuk kepada identiti pembunuh ayahnya.

programme.desc: Rompakan yang kecil menjadi huru-hara, apabila pencuri berakhir di istana lama dan menemui sumpahan purba yang melindungi hartanya. Entiti ghaib secara aktif cuba menghalang mereka daripada mencari emas, atau adakah mereka?

programme.title: The Invoking
programme.desc: Selepas mewarisi rumah daripada keluarga yang tidak pernah dikenalinya, Samantha Harris (Trin Miller) dan tiga rakannya menuju ke Sader Ridge luar bandar untuk memeriksa harta itu. Tidak lama selepas tiba, Sam mula mengalami penglihatan mengerikan tentang kekejaman ganas dan kejahatan yang tidak terkata. Diganggu oleh kuasa jahat yang mengepungnya, Sam mengalami mimpi ngeri apabila syaitan dari masa lalunya enggan terus dikebumikan lagi.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.desc: Akil yang dihinggap sakit gatal-gatal pulang ke kampung untuk mencari penawar. Akil berubat dengan bomoh Tok Misai dan juga diberi sebentuk cincin permata hijau. Malangnya keesokan hari, Tok Misai terbunuh semasa berkelahi dengan Pawang Anjang Itam yang sedang mencari cincin 4 keramat yang berada dalam milik Tok Misai. Sepulangnya ke bandar, Akil dapati gatal-gatalnya hilang dan diberitahu kepada kawannya Nabil. Nabil mengingatkan Akil supaya berjaga-jaga kerana kebiasaannya Tok Bomoh ada membela hantu. Akil mula percaya cakap Nabil kerana dia pernah diusik oleh lembaga pada waktu malam. Akil pulang sekali lagi ke kampung untuk menemui Tok Misai tetapi diberitahu Tok Misai telah mati terbunuh. Di masa sama Siti anak Tok Misai sedang mencari siapa yang terakhir berubat dengan ayahnya.

Trisya seorang gadis yang mendambakan untuk dicintai, tetapi apabila bertemu dengannya barulah dia sedar bahawa cinta sejati bukanlah hamparan bunga mawar. Freez adalah seorang lelaki yang riang yang hanya berfikir tentang melepak dengan rakan-rakannya dan menjadi gembira, manakala Lara adalah seorang yang bersemangat bebas yang mahu membuat jalannya di dunia sendiri. Mereka berempat bertemu di Wira Cinta, sebuah kelab yang dimiliki oleh Kak Pora di mana mereka semua belajar seni mempertahankan diri dan juga mengenali diri mereka sendiri, apabila Pinto, abang ipar Firman dari masa lalunya yang kelam muncul di kelab itu dan menuntut bahawa Firman kembali kepada kumpulan itu atau menghadapi akibatnya.

programme.title: Nayang
programme.desc: Seorang penulis skrip bernama Eysha sedang mencari bahan untuk menulis kisah misteri yang berlaku di sebuah kampung terpencil bernama Kampung Nayang. Di sana dia bertemu Nek Som yang tahu akan kisah itu. Menurut cerita Nek Som, di kampung itu dahulu tinggal seorang wanita bernama Nayang yang sering diganggu Jalak dan rakan-rakannya ketika suaminya dipenjara akibat difitnah. Ketika itulah berlaku satu tragedi sehingga mengakibatkan kekecohan di seluruh kampung itu.

programme.title: Misteri Rumah Tua
programme.desc: Dendam lama mula terbalas apabila hadirnya sekumpulan remaja ke sebuah rumah lama yang dihuni roh wanita. Sebuah pembunuhan kejam telah berlaku di rumah tersebut apabila dia dirogol dan dibunuh ketika sedang sarat mengandung. Wanita tersebut ingin membalas dendam kerana ketidakadilan yang telah berlaku ketika dirinya masih hidup. Bapa kepada salah seorang dari kumpulan remaja tersebut pula pernah terlibat dengan pembunuhan kejam wanita itu yang menaikkan lagi rasa marah roh tersebut. Pelbagai insiden menyeramkan mula terjadi di rumah itu.

programme.title: Bapak Borek Anak Rintik
programme.desc: Johan merupakan seorang pemuda yang memiliki kelebihan semulajadi dari segi kepantasan dan tenaga. Johan bertekad untuk mencari ayahnya yang tidak pernah ditemuinya sejak dilahirkan. Dalam pencarian itu Johan telah menyelamatkan Osman yang sedang ditimpa masalah. Johan yakin Osman ialah ayahnya yang dicari cari selama ini. Perkenalan dengan Osman telah melibatkan Johan dalam masalah yang lebih besar. Johan yang lurus bendul itu telah dipergunakan Osman untuk melakukan tugas-tugas mengintip Julia, gadis pisau cukur. Keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara apabila Johan berkenalan dan dengan Fiza.

Dalam masa yang sama, Sunny mencintai seorang penyanyi baharu yang bernama Natasha.

Dalam perjalanannya menuju Kota Singa, Sudin bertemu dengan Zaharah dan Mayon di sebuah kawasan rehat dan menumpangkan mereka berdua ke Johor Bahru. Tanpa disedari, Sudin telah kehilangan pasportnya dan dia terperangkap dalam satu sindiket pemalsuan dokumen. Pelbagai kejadian berlaku sehingga Sudin dianggap sebagai pendatang asing tanpa izin.

Profesor Hamdan dan Ramlah serta anak mereka, Saiful dan Marina berpindah ke sebuah banglo lama di tepi laut. Mereka hidup aman dan damai bersama di banglo tersebut. Dia mempunyai rancangan untuk menggoda dua lagi gadis baru sebagai mangsanya. Rancangan Badul memakan diri apabila dia sendiri terpaksa menikahi mereka - cubaannya telah memerangkap dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Nayang
programme.desc: Seorang penulis skrip bernama Eysha sedang mencari bahan untuk menulis kisah misteri yang berlaku di sebuah kampung terpencil bernama Kampung Nayang. Di sana dia bertemu Nek Som yang tahu akan kisah itu. Menurut cerita Nek Som, di kampung itu dahulu tinggal seorang wanita bernama Nayang yang sering diganggu Jalak dan rakan-rakannya ketika suaminya dipenjara akibat difitnah. Ketika itulah berlaku satu tragedi sehingga mengakibatkan kekecohan di seluruh kampung itu.

programme.title: Misteri Rumah Tua
programme.desc: Dendam lama mula terbalas apabila hadirnya sekumpulan remaja ke sebuah rumah lama yang dihuni roh wanita. Sebuah pembunuhan kejam telah berlaku di rumah tersebut apabila dia dirogol dan dibunuh ketika sedang sarat mengandung. Wanita tersebut ingin membalas dendam kerana ketidakadilan yang telah berlaku ketika dirinya masih hidup. Bapa kepada salah seorang dari kumpulan remaja tersebut pula pernah terlibat dengan pembunuhan kejam wanita itu yang menaikkan lagi rasa marah roh tersebut. Pelbagai insiden menyeramkan mula terjadi di rumah itu.

programme.title: Bapak Borek Anak Rintik
programme.desc: Johan merupakan seorang pemuda yang memiliki kelebihan semulajadi dari segi kepantasan dan tenaga. Johan bertekad untuk mencari ayahnya yang tidak pernah ditemuinya sejak dilahirkan. Dalam pencarian itu Johan telah menyelamatkan Osman yang sedang ditimpa masalah. Johan yakin Osman ialah ayahnya yang dicari cari selama ini. Perkenalan dengan Osman telah melibatkan Johan dalam masalah yang lebih besar. Johan yang lurus bendul itu telah dipergunakan Osman untuk melakukan tugas-tugas mengintip Julia, gadis pisau cukur. Keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara apabila Johan berkenalan dan dengan Fiza.

programme.title: Suratan Kasih
programme.desc: Sunny mengalami tekanan jiwa selepas melihat ibunya yang sedang berzina mati dibunuh ayahnya sendiri. Apabila meningkat dewasa, Sunny menjadi seorang pembunuh bersiri di sebalik kerjayanya sebagai komposer dan pemuzik. Mangsanya ialah golongan perempuan yang melakukan perbuatan zina. Dalam masa yang sama, Sunny mencintai seorang penyanyi baharu yang bernama Natasha.

programme.title: Dendam Pelamin
programme.desc: Hubungan cinta antara Marissa dan Saiful putus seminggu sebelum mereka berkahwin. Ini kerana Saiful tidak mencintai Marissa dan memilih untuk bersama Nani. Sebelum mereka berpisah, Saiful sempat menyonglap wang syarikat sebanyak RM250 ribu dan enggan membayar semula kepada Marissa. Perkara ini menyebabkan Marissa menaruh dendam terhadap Saiful dan Nani dan merancang sesuatu untuk membalas dendam.

programme.title: Jengka
programme.desc: Nini mengalami keguguran semasa melarikan diri di ladang kelapa sawit. Namun, satu perkara aneh terjadi apabila bayinya dikatakan masih hidup dan dilarikan oleh penunggu. Orang kampung berusaha membantu mencari Nini dan anaknya, namun perkara seram terjadi sepanjang pencarian mereka.

programme.title: Aku Bukan Pendatang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sudin yang mendapat tugasan untuk menghantar kereta pejabatnya ke Singapura. Dalam perjalanannya menuju Kota Singa, Sudin bertemu dengan Zaharah dan Mayon di sebuah kawasan rehat dan menumpangkan mereka berdua ke Johor Bahru. Tanpa disedari, Sudin telah kehilangan pasportnya dan dia terperangkap dalam satu sindiket pemalsuan dokumen. Pelbagai kejadian berlaku sehingga Sudin dianggap sebagai pendatang asing tanpa izin.

programme.title: Rahsia
programme.desc: Dihantui gangguan misteri, sepasang suami isteri mula mencari punca kepada gangguan tersebut. Profesor Hamdan dan Ramlah serta anak mereka, Saiful dan Marina berpindah ke sebuah banglo lama di tepi laut. Mereka hidup aman dan damai bersama di banglo tersebut. Namun tragedi melanda apabila Marina lemas di laut dan meninggal dunia - dari situlah bermulanya kejadian aneh.

programme.title: Alahai Kekasihku
programme.desc: Rini seorang wanita berbadan besar yang ingin mengurangkan berat badannya. Namun dia sering gagal untuk berbuat sedemikian kerana dia suka makan. Di pejabat, Rini sering bertikam lidah dengan Norman yang selalu menyakitkan hatinya. Dalam masa yang sama, Rini jatuh cinta dengan seorang lelaki yang dikenalinya di internet. Apabila mereka bercadang untuk berjumpa buat kali pertama, Rini berusaha dengan lebih giat untuk menjadi kurus.

programme.desc: A large-scale tourism programme that is designed to present rich tourism resources in China and around the world

programme.title: China News

programme.title: The 59th Broadcast Golden Bell Awards (M) Ep1
programme.desc: The 59th Golden Bell Awards is one of the annual events of the Taiwan media industry in 2024 to reward the outstanding Taiwanese radio practitioners in 2024. Who will seize the ultimate glory? The excitement is palpable!

programme.title: Dear Mom (M) Ep1011
programme.desc: Feng-Yi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, Shu-An, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. Yi-Wan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. Qing-Qing may be having an affair with a married man. Xiao-Xi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of "the others." An-Qing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: 2024 Penghu Music Festival (M) Ep1
programme.desc: Get ready for a sensational event featuring a dazzling light show and a star-studded lineup of performers, making this the ultimate music extravaganza of Penghu this autumn. The 2024 Penghu Music Festival continues the momentum with the theme 'Sing with the Breeze,' calling all passionate music lovers to join in, sing their hearts out, soak in the stunning views, indulge in delicious local treats, and enjoy the most epic music party ever!

programme.desc: In the new culinary show Just Eat, celebrities reveal their favorite chefs and memorable dishes. This series explores how these culinary experiences have impacted their lives, from overcoming personal struggles to finding new career paths. Join us to discover the flavors and stories that resonate with these well-known personalities.

programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Death Notice
programme.desc: A serial killer leaves death notices in a city, stating when, how and who he will murder. Even if the victims report it to the police and receive protection, the killer can still break through and execute them. While the police sets up a special task force in response, they expose an even bigger conspiracy behind.

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Chois actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: Lucky Star 2015
programme.desc: When a talent manager meets a guy whose voice resembles the famous comedian Stephen Chow, things starts to stir up in the show biz. "Lucky Star 2015" is a hilarious comedy starring actors from both Hong Kong and Taiwan, including Eric Tsang, Dada Chan and Wong Cho Lam.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: Love is the only Answer
programme.desc: At BO (Charmaine Sheh) and CHEONG (Alex Fong) wedding reception, the projected was initially showing their journey of love, but suddenly a flash of a clip of CHEONG and a sexy girl being intimate came up. BO calmly ran up to the stage and announced that the wedding is cancelled. The incident rapidly became a hot topic on the internet. Within a year, back to being single again, BO and the living life happily CHEONG maintains a good relationship. One day, CHEONG decided to play with love and took BO to participate in a swinging party. The conservative BO initially wanted to leave, but after being bribed by CHEONG, she helpless and stayed. At the swinging party, the two encounter KIT (Him Law) and his wife MAN LAI (Kelly Fu). The 4 of them develop a romantic and hot relationship... At another wedding reception, when th projector plays the groom (Jason Chan) and bride (Rose Chan)'s heartwarming clips, a flash of another clip that does not want to be seen comes up...

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: The Bride With White Hair
programme.desc: Based on the 1954 martial arts novel by acclaimed author Liang Yu-sang, this film details the tragic romance between wild swordsman Zhuo Yi-hang and rival cult assassin Lien Ni-chang, with a dark, erotic and visually stunning twist.

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his fathers remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn

programme.title: Ip Man 3
programme.desc: When some gangsters led by a ruthless American property developer force a school to sell their land, Ip Man fights to protect it. Subsequently, Ip Man is challenged by another Wing Chun master Zhang Tian Zhi for the Grandmaster title. Ip Man accepts the challenge for the sake of his family and disciples, and wins the duel for the title.

programme.title: Everything is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met. When Pan discovers that his daughter is being abused by Hua, he vows to save her but eventually fall into their trap

programme.title: Chilli Laugh Story
programme.desc: Coba is forced to work at home during COVID-19 and fights with his family every day. He decides to turn his mothers chilli sauce into a trendy commodity to keep his family occupied. With his mother, father and aunt making the chilli sauce together, the family sells it online and the business grows beyond their imagination.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: Based on the true story of David Ki, one of Asias top rock climbers who lost everything when a motorcycle accident crippled him. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found a way of scaling the dizzying peaks again by becoming a wheelchair-bound athlete and soon reached the peak of Lion Rock!

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tungs mad fate?

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Cliff Walkers
programme.desc: The first spy thriller movie by famous Director Zhang Yi Mou, this film follows four Communist Party special agents who embark on a secret operation in the Japanese puppet state of Manchukuo in 1932. Sold out by a traitor, the agents, who split up into two teams, find themselves surrounded by threats on all sides. Can they complete their mission?

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quins trust, Nick becomes his protg and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubs top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Wits Of The Brats
programme.desc: Tou Kuan is a wealthy Kwangtung brat with a good kung fu background, he has only one ambition: to pit his wits against three shady masters of the North. The first, conman Che Tsai. The second, a professional romantic dubbed The Terrific. Terrific introduces Tou Kuan to his third rival, Thief Shih San-shou.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends help.

programme.title: The Naval Commandos
programme.desc: The Chinese Navy is attempting to defend its coastline from a Japanese attack, they send their commando unit led by Cui Hsia into the mainland to enlist help to thwart the Japanese before they attack. The commandos enlist the help of Song San and Shiao Liu to kill the Japanese officers led by Shan Mao and destroy their attacking ships.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: Famous Kung Fu Pole master Red Eagle, is kidnapped by a villain one day. His disciple Meng, vows to rescue him. On his way, Meng encounters a greedy but great martial artist who agrees to join him in the rescue. Even though the two have extremely different personalities, they manage to team up and fight the villain in a final showdown.

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Changs. On the Changs farm, she meets their two sons, the youngest daughter and a young artist, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: The Pure And The Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fangs fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandmas pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chiefs daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: Till the End of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: Fangs of the Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Apartment for Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: Rendezvous With Death
programme.desc: Sun Chung had been recognized as an expert comedy and crime thriller director, but he was to gain even greater acclaim for his soulful, powerful, intelligent, and beautifully-made martial arts epics. This stands alongside The Deadly Breaking Sword and The Kung-fu Instructor as one of his very best. It's not so much the plot - a master swordsman protects a treasure chest on a dangerous journey - that makes this great, but what Sun does with it, inspiring the cast and crew to some of their finest work.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: Pursuit of a Killer
programme.desc: The charm of Pursuit Of A Killer lies in the long awaited reunion of Five Venoms duo, Lo Meng and Sun Chien; Lo Meng, who plays a Mainland Chinese criminal escapee to Hong Kong in search of a better life, and a cop (Sun Chien) who helps him adjust to Hong Kong life while tracking down his mysterious killer at the same time.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: The Killer Has No Return
programme.desc: Professional killer Lui goes to Malaysia after completing his mission of killing the big boss of a Hong Kong gang. His next target is a groom who is throwing his wedding banquet at a hotel in Chinatown. Just when Lui takes aim at his target, another victim instead of the groom is shot, and he becomes a scapegoat in this mystery assassination.

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: The Battle Wizard
programme.desc: Dali Prince Tuan Yu knows nothing about martial arts, but leaves the palace for the martial arts world. He meets a snake sorceress and his mysterious half-sister. Through various misadventures, Tuan Yu gains invincible power by sucking the cobras blood and swallowing the magic toad, eventually defeating his fathers old rival.

programme.title: Between Tears and Smiles
programme.desc: Fan Jia Shu is a kind-hearted student who is smitten with Shen, a heart-rending love song singer. However, he is not the only one who has eyes for Shen. The Generals henchmen are also determined to present the songstress to their superior as a gift. Fan receives help from an unexpected person just in time to save the woman he loves.

programme.title: Journey of the Doomed
programme.desc: Journey Of The Doomed stars Tung Wei as a knight that finds himself protecting the life of a beautiful young lady, the lost Emperor's daughter and stalked by a bunch of assassins headed by kung fu actress extraordinaire Hui Ying-Hung.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: The Casino
programme.desc: After being separated for many years, two childhood lovers meet in a possibly mythical "Lucky Casino" and vow to rid the establishment of the corrupt military generals, criminals and extortionists!

programme.title: Hell Has No Boundary
programme.desc: Cheng Chung (Derek Yee) and May (Liu Hsueh-hua), a pair of lovers working on the police force, camp on an outlying island. Awakened by a strange sound, May goes out onto the beach where a violent frenzy grips her. After her return from leave, May insists Inspector Wang (Yueh Hua) in a bid to rescue some hostages. She shoots the thug under most peculiar circumstances. Then a series of tragedies occur. Her two colleagues die mangled in a lift accident and Inspector Wang is injured at his desk by a snake. Wang's exorcist sister (Hsia Ping), who performs rites for him, also dies in an accident. And so does a fortune-teller who refused to read May's fortune.

programme.title: Twin Blades Of Doom
programme.desc: A retired martial artist is forced to return with a vengeance after his family and friends are murdered by the evil Ghost Gang. He decides to challenge the gangs leader to a deadly duel so as to take revenge. Can he defeat the ruthless leader in the end?

programme.title: Judgement of an Assassin
programme.desc: An evil clan plans a discord so as to dominate the martial arts world. Their masked assassins massacre another clan and one of the assassins is arrested and brought to trial at a tribunal of all the clans. What judgement will they make and can they uncover the truth?

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor Tang Ming Huang, who is so besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister Yang Guo Zhong, the brother of Yang Gui Fei. The Prime Minister is corrupt and cruel to the army, causing them to revolt and endanger the throne. Yang Gui Fei is also implicated and kills herself.

programme.title: Mad Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Master Chen was an esteemed Monkey Kung Fu master, until he is framed and crippled by a ruthless villain and ends up becoming a wandering artiste. When Chen meets a young man, Little Monkey, on the streets, he decides to teach him all his monkey kung fu moves. Both men eventually team up to avenge Chens past insult.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: The Singing Killer
programme.desc: Chiang Yi is blackmailed into a jewelry heist by his former boss, who threatens to expose his shady past. Complications arise when he discovers his first love works at the store.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Black Tavern
programme.desc: This sword-filled thriller centres on The Black Tavern an inn where the down and dirty meet to plot nefarious doings. A bunch of villains are lured to the inn by a rumour about a valuable treasure being hidden there. After all the backstabbing and killings, they realise that it is a trap created to wipe them out once and for all

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: Five Elements Ninjas
programme.desc: The film is about a Chinese martial arts school finds itself outclassed by their rivals, they hire elite ninja from Japan to destroy the school. The lone survivor of the massacre learns the secrets of ninjutsu and seeks revenge against the ninja.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 - July-August - a Time of Migration Ep4
programme.desc: Witness some of the planets most dramatic natural shifts in July, from the Arctic ice sheets that come crashing down during the summer melt to the feeding frenzy when sockeye salmon reach the end of their journey in Alaska.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 - September-October - a Time of Activation Ep5
programme.desc: Travel around the world to see another seasonal change unfold. The Northern Hemisphere moves into autumn, while Australia witnesses a rebirth of life, and mating humpbacks fill the warming tropical seas of Tonga.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 - November-December - Full Circle Ep6
programme.desc: Witness some of the most incredible natural events in November, from the millions of Monarch butterflies that converge in Mexicos forests to the deep fog that shrouds the city of Dubai, signalling the start of winter.

programme.title: Colombia's Wild Coast 1 - Snake Prison Island Ep1
programme.desc: Gorgona was once home to Colombias Alcatraz. Modelled on Nazi concentration camps, prisoners dreamt of escape. See the islands stunning wildlife through the eyes of a convict on the run, the monkeys, snakes and sloths whove now reclaimed the land.

programme.title: Colombia's Wild Coast 1 - March of the Crabs Ep2
programme.desc: On the island of Providencia, a black crab begins the mission of her life, escorting 80,000 eggs from her home, on a 3 km hike to the coast. Join her, and millions of her clan, on a journey fraught with danger, where chances of survival are slim.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - Into the Darkness Ep3
programme.desc: Stay up late as the northern team attaches an activity tag to a bull shark and finds out what this night owl does after sunset. Then dive 80 meters deep with the southern team, who are hoping to put a satellite tracker on a female great white.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - The Social Network Ep4
programme.desc: Ponder shark community hierarchies as the northern team studies how young blacktips learn social and survival skills. Then rush to Rainbow Beach with the southern team, who are eager to witness the sand tiger sharks most elusive behaviour: mating.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - Detour Ep5
programme.desc: Travel to the ends of Australias shark highways. Find out if Greenly Island in the south is a truck stop for migrating great whites, then search for proof of a genetic connection between northern bull sharks and their cooler-climate cousins.

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 - Snares Islands/ Tini Heke Ep1
programme.desc: Venture to the pristine wilderness of the Snares Islands, a remote animal sanctuary protected from the turbulent sea. Hop along with a colony of Snares crested penguins, soar with giant petrels and sooty shearwaters, and roar with giant sea lions.

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 - Otago Peninsula/ Muaupoko Ep2
programme.desc: Set sail for New Zealands Otago Peninsula, a breeding refuge for endangered seabirds and marine mammals. Watch as sea lions, albatrosses, red-billed gulls, white-fronted terns, and fairy prions find mates, then nurture the next generation.

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 - Top of the South/ Te Tau Ihu Ep3
programme.desc: Uncover a land of opposites atop New Zealands South Island, where one of the worlds longest sandbars attracts bar-tailed godwits and hungry pilot whales, and drowned river valleys provide a buffet for dusky dolphins and New Zealand fur seals.

programme.desc: South Africas greatest wetland, Lake St. Lucia, provides sustenance for animals that depend on standing water, including hippos, crocs, and countless water birds. But during a drought, the system faces challenges that have devastating consequences.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - The Borderlands Ep1
programme.desc: Where the mountains cross international borders, herds of elk and moose live side by side with predators like bears and wolves. The predator/prey relationship is a delicate balance, and the perfect place to see it in action is the Kootenay area of the Rocky Mountains.

programme.title: Great Lakes Wild 1 - Isle Royale Ep1
programme.desc: Since the 1900s, this uninhabited island in Lake Superior has been a constant battleground between moose and wolves. Scientists have been watching closely since 1953, making it one of the oldest research projects in the country. We go with lead researcher Rolf Peterson as he gets a band of volunteers to scour the island for moose bones, trying to piece together population numbers after a long winter.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 3 - Hard Lessons Ep3
programme.desc: Shudder as food-obsessed Beni gets a dramatic, educational smackdown from the local dominant male, Petruk. See spoiled rich kid Spanser, a former illegal pet, try to tamp down his sweet tooth before roguish Bumi goes on a wild joyride with Greta.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 3 - Outbreak Alert Ep4
programme.desc: Race to contain a case of malaria brought in by orphaned infant Cesia, then assess surrogate mum Sris plan to help Bumi. See the positive influence of Daput, a wild orangutan mum, on the college females before a shocking thief raids the food store.

programme.title: Carpathian Predators 1 - Realm of the Wolf Ep2
programme.desc: In the remote wilderness of the Carpathian Mountains lives an elusive predator that has inspired awe and fear throughout history: the Eurasian wolf. Discover the vital role that these once-misunderstood hunters play in protecting their ecosystem.

programme.title: Gangs of Lemur Island 1 - Risk and Reward Ep3
programme.desc: The drought is finally over, but traversing the forest for food is still a gamble. See some leaders take the risk, leaving home territories undefended to feast on a cicada boom. When they return, trespassers are ready for a fight.

programme.title: Gangs of Lemur Island 1 - The Road to Independence Ep4
programme.desc: As the babies grow, new power struggles break out in each troop. Watch as every member, from fierce Queen Crystal to low-ranking Erica, jockeys for position. Meanwhile, the babies start to understand how allies and enemies will shape their future.
